### [FALHA] Campo name ausente
# Esperado: 422 Validation Error com campo name nos issues
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/services
Authorization: Bearer {{accessTokenAbmael}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Sem nome",
  "durationMinutes": 30,
  "priceInCents": 5000,
  "isActive": true
}

###

### [FALHA] durationMinutes zero (inválido)
# Esperado: 422 Validation Error com campo durationMinutes nos issues
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/services
Authorization: Bearer {{accessTokenAbmael}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Serviço inválido",
  "description": "Duração zero",
  "durationMinutes": 0,
  "priceInCents": 5000,
  "isActive": true
}

###

